data.description: Enjoy watching the deer in the morning while drinking your coffee on the back deck! Fantastic .60 acre partially wooded lot located in the cul-de-sac. Well laid out 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a family room and an additional living area that the would be great for in home office or formal living room. The storage building in the back yard is a great size to store your tools or create outside entertainment area. This home is waiting for your imagination, perfect way to create equity by doing updates yourself.
